            . I am the niece of Mrs. Fouseca, my uncle lives in <placeName id="t18090412-60-crimeloc366">Newmarket-street, Wapping</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18090412-60-crimeloc366" type="placeName" value="Newmarket-street, Wapping"></interp>
